content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1262.33 - Presence of at least two approved fire extinguishers required

State Regulations

During fuel handling operations in connection with
any aircraft at an air terminal, at least two dry chemical extinguishers
(20-pound) or the equivalent shall be immediately available for use in
connection therewith. Notes
